{"lemma":"وَجْز","slug":"وَجْز","root":"#.ج.ز","root_slug":"_-ج-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ج-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41709","n41711"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D8%B2"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to abbreviate, to summarize, to cut short (a speech, etc.)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be swift, to be prompt, to be short and precise"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"short, brief, swift"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41709","headword_ar":"وَجُزَ","root":"wjz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaAzapN","text_ar":"وَجَازَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajozN","text_ar":"وَجْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an expression, or speech, or language,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was brief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an expression]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was brief, and quickly intelligible:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man's speech)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was of few words;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awojaza","text_ar":"اَوْجَزَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of language: (A, K:) or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(language)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was of few words, with eloquence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajuza fiY manoTiqihi","text_ar":"وَجُزَ فِى مَنْطِقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY kalaAmihi","text_ar":"فى كَلَامِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaza fiyhi","text_ar":"وَجَزَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajizu","text_ar":"يَجِزُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaAzapN","text_ar":"وَجَازَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) of the former verb; (TA;) and [of the latter]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajozN","text_ar":"وَجْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wujuwzN","text_ar":"وُجُوزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awjz","text_ar":"اوجز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was brief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concise, in his speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTonaba","text_ar":"اَطْنَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was of few words in his speech:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K: *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was brief, and quickly intelligible, in his language:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awjz","text_ar":"اوجز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was quick and brief"},{"kind":"text","text":"in speaking. (Nh, TA.) See this latter verb below.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaza","text_ar":"وَجَزَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~afoZa","text_ar":"اللَّفْظَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4."}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","TA","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n41711","headword_ar":"وَجْزٌ","root":"wjz","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quickness; speed; haste."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) As an epithet, applied to a man, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick of motion"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in that which he begins:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a camel. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, applied to a man, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prompt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick, in giving."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajozN","text_ar":"وَجْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajiyzN","text_ar":"وَجِيزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAjizN","text_ar":"وَاجِزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muwjazN","text_ar":"مُوجَزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muwjizN","text_ar":"مُوجِزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) applied to an expression, (Msb,) or language, (S, A, K, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Brief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly intel-ligible:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of few words:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abridged:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xafiyfN","text_ar":"خَفِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and keeping within just,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moderate, bounds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and all these epithets (all but the last accord. to the K, and the last also accord. to the TA,) are likewise applied to the thing, or an affair, [app. meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (K, TA:) and the first is also applied to a gift, and to beneficence, meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S","A","Msb"]}]}}